title: SVENGOOLIE-The Mad Magician 1954- V. Price Aired 3/17/2018 WIDE
description:
SVENGOOLIE- The Mad Magician 1954  Vincent Price Aired 3/17/2018  

Sven's original showing broadcast a Full-Frame version of the film, I chose to use a widescreen dvd offering proper aspect ratio, better picture, while preserving the original broadcast as closely as possible( to the frame) .


" In this horror film, originally released in 3-D, a magician goes on the rampage after a rival steels his secrets and his wife. His next performance(s) involve the usual magic tricks--and death... as he begins killing his quarry in very strange ways."

CAST:
Vincent Price
Eva Gabor
John Emery


Features a interview with Makeup & Effects Artist , Michael Burnett and Senator Jeff Van Drew from New Jersey. 

MANY probs here in the US w/ TPB....get thru to the site with what I can
